subject: Australian Open (Golf)
Golf
lead_paragraph: Yani Tseng of Taiwan won the Women’s Australian Open in Melbourne, making birdies on 7 of the last 12 holes for a seven-under-par 66 and a three-stroke victory over the 2009 winner, Laura Davies of England.
